========,2,Transportation.
Big Bear City Airport is a general aviation airport in Big Bear City.
There are no commercial air services to this airport, although at least two airlines, including Trans World Airlines, have served Big Bear in the past.
This airport may also be used for medical evacuations, and as a base for forest-fighting aircraft when there are fires close by.
